540
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:15,749
- That sounds good. - Yes.

541
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:16,809
- Do you mean water spinach? - We just need garlic.

542
00:21:16,810 --> 00:21:18,409
Yes, it's water spinach. We just need garlic.

543
00:21:18,410 --> 00:21:19,919
- We can add garlic... - Oyster sauce.

544
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:21,220
and oyster sauce.

545
00:21:21,450 --> 00:21:22,450
I'm hungry.

546
00:21:22,451 --> 00:21:24,289
Does talking about food make your stomach react?

547
00:21:24,290 --> 00:21:25,290
(Talking about it makes her hungry.)

548
00:21:25,290 --> 00:21:26,290
I'm very hungry.

549
00:21:26,291 --> 00:21:29,629
I can't wait to find out local food...

550
00:21:29,630 --> 00:21:31,230
in the Philippines.

551
00:21:32,630 --> 00:21:37,070
(At what kind of place will the siblings have their first meal?)

552
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:38,930
Oh, is it a cow?

553
00:21:40,340 --> 00:21:41,800
(Full of anticipation)

554
00:21:43,170 --> 00:21:45,140
