555
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:49,280
(Filled with authentic Filipino vibes)

556
00:21:58,050 --> 00:22:00,690
(Packed with a variety of dishes you can only try in the Philippines)

557
00:22:01,920 --> 00:22:03,530
(There's also alimango.)

558
00:22:04,190 --> 00:22:05,329
(A local favorite loved by both locals and tourists)

559
00:22:05,330 --> 00:22:06,799
There's also seafood.

560
00:22:06,800 --> 00:22:09,169
- It looks like a tasty restaurant. - That sounds delicious.

561
00:22:09,170 --> 00:22:10,170
(Welcome)

562
00:22:10,430 --> 00:22:11,899
(The four siblings take a seat.)

563
00:22:11,900 --> 00:22:13,669
Don't you think you'll pass out...

564
00:22:13,670 --> 00:22:14,799
