793
00:30:57,860 --> 00:31:02,500
(There are also fresh vegetables.)

794
00:31:03,230 --> 00:31:05,630
- There are napa cabbages. - Shall we get one?

795
00:31:06,770 --> 00:31:09,810
(The siblings plan to make kimchi.)

796
00:31:10,310 --> 00:31:13,140
Mangoes are 150 pesos per kilogram.

797
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:16,010
If it's 150 pesos per kilogram,

798
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:18,680
- That's affordable. - it's not bad.

799
00:31:19,010 --> 00:31:21,650
(Let's get some immediately.)

